<h2>How was your seller experience?</h2>

<p>Hi <%= customerName || "there" %>,</p>

<p>
  <strong><%= vendorName %></strong> has completed their part of order
  <strong><%= orderNumber || "your order" %></strong>.
</p>

<p>
  We’d love to hear how it went. Your rating helps other customers shop with confidence and helps the seller improve.
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= reviewUrl %>" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;border-radius:10px;background:#202020;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">
    Rate this seller
  </a>
</p>

<p style="margin-top:16px;">
  You can leave a star rating, add a comment, and attach photos if you’d like.
</p>
